<h3>About Tracks</h3>
<p>Learning Sales Tracking has never been easier using tracks and it’s amazing drag and drop interface. Tracks is focused on helping small businesses keep up to date with monthly sales and revenue that integrates with both Highrise CRM and Google Apps.</p>

<h3>Project Request</h3>
<p>Tracks provided several comps showcasing their new design that was in need of development. It was requested that the libraries listed for this project be an absolute requirement to fit in with their currrent platform. Before the project began it was suggested an atomic guide be created to keep track of components that were already in the system or could be used again in other contexts.</p>
<p>The approach to Tracks’ interface started with each component investigated and isolated using the principles outlined by <a href="http://atomicdesign.bradfrost.com">Brad Frost</a>. These LEGO-like pieces would eventually be constructed together to form a larger distinctive part of the interface.</p>
