<h3>Process</h3>
<p>Prototypes were created with <a href="https://www.invisionapp.com">InVision</a> to build and structure a working and functional application interface. Since this was a build from the ground up, SVG was used throughout along with flexbox to assist in quick and easy layout typically resorted to with floats and margin trickery.</p>
